# Homework 1 – Search and Heuristics

## Overview
This assignment focuses on solving a colored blocks tower problem using search algorithms in Python.

The project includes state representation, neighbor generation, goal testing, open/closed set handling, and heuristic design for optimal search.

## Topics
- A* search
- State-space search
- Heuristic functions
- Open and closed sets
- Neighbor generation
- Optimal pathfinding

## Files
- `heuristics.py` – heuristic implementations
- `color_blocks_state.py` – state representation and transitions
- `search.py` – search data structures and logic
- `search_node.py` – search node implementation
- `main.py` – program entry point

## Skills Demonstrated
- Problem modeling as a search problem
- Heuristic design and optimization
- Efficient search implementation
- Python programming for AI
